OL,3,CThe chancellor's choice between
OL,4,CNational Insurance and income tax cuts
OL,6,FInevitably therefore cutting the rate
OL,7,Fof income tax costs #2bn a year more
OL,8,Fthan cutting NI for each penny
OL,9,Freduction. So bribing more potential
OL,10,Fvoters isn't cheap.
OL,12,FMy hunch, as I said , is he'll do a
OL,13,Fpenny off each. But as of now, that is
OL,14,Fhow it smells rather than what I know.
OL,16,FWhat I know is that 2p in the pound is
OL,17,Fcoming off these taxes on income in
OL,18,Fsome combination or other.
