OL,3,CThe chancellor's choice between
OL,4,CNational Insurance and income tax cuts
OL,6,FTorsten Bell from the think tank the
OL,7,FResolution Foundation said in a post
OL,8,Fon X that Jeremy Hunt is "choosing a
OL,9,Ftotally new approach to the shape of
OL,10,Ftax policy".
OL,12,FHe compares Mr Hunt's tax policy to
OL,13,Fthat of former Chancellor George
OL,14,FOsborne, saying: "I think everyone who
OL,15,Fworks on tax policy will recognise
OL,16,Fthat Jeremy Hunt's is by far the
OL,17,Fbetter tax reform strategy - whatever
OL,18,Fthey think about whether the tax cuts
OL,19,Fcan be afforded in the current
OL,20,Fclimate."
