OL,6,FUPDATE 1415:
OL,8,FThe Times' Political Editor Steven
OL,9,FSwinford is right that Chancellor will
OL,10,Ftomorrow cut employee national
OL,11,Finsurance by 2p.
OL,13,FThe distributional impact, i.e winners
OL,14,Fand losers, are interesting. According
OL,15,Fto the Resolution Foundation, those
OL,16,Fearning up to #19,000 would be net
OL,17,Flosers because of freezing of
OL,18,Fthresholds.
