OL,6,FThose earning just under #50,000 would
OL,7,Fbe biggest winners, with net gain of
OL,8,F#1200.
OL,10,FAbove that threshold the benefits
OL,11,Fshrink in relative terms. And remember
OL,12,Fthe NI cut hands zilch to pensioners
OL,13,Fand those with so-called unearned
OL,14,Fincome.
